---

<div class="scroll-reveal">
  <div class="relative bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-card border border-warm-100/60 overflow-hidden">
    
    <!-- Detalhe decorativo -->
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-300 via-warm-300 to-gold-300"></div>
    
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-8 items-center">
      
      <!-- Avatar -->
      <div class="relative flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-cream-200 to-warm-100 border-4 border-white shadow-warm flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-5xl">👩‍👧‍👦</span>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-1 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-400 to-gold-500 text-white text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full shadow-sm whitespace-nowrap">
          Mãe de 2
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bio -->
      <div class="text-center md:text-left flex-grow space-y-3">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl text-warm-900">Mariana Reis</h3>
          <p class="text-xs text-warm-400 font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mt-1">Curadora Editorial Independente</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-warm-600 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-xl">
          Depois do Léo (4 anos) e da Sofia (1 ano), senti na pele o desespero de montar o enxoval. Comprei carrinho pesado que não cabia no porta-malas, me arrependi, testei mais de 10 modelos de amigas e familiares. Criei este guia para poupar o seu tempo e o seu bolso dos mesmos erros que eu cometi.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center md:justify-start gap-x-5 gap-y-2 text-xs">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-warm-500">
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-sage-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Sem favorecimento de marcas
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-warm-500">
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-sage-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Análises do dia a dia real
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-1.5 text-warm-500">
            <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-sage-500" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
            Links auditados Amazon BR
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
